                <mxCell id="t-note" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:left;padding:5px;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ghi chú bảo mật:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Path validation ngăn directory escape&lt;br&gt;• SQLite chỉ cho phép read-only queries&lt;br&gt;• Python code chạy trong subprocess có timeout&lt;br&gt;• Tất cả path phải relative từ context_dir&lt;/div&gt;" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;size=14;verticalAlign=top;align=center;fillColor=#ffffcc;strokeColor=#d6b656;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
